						<p>Chāḷukya-Chōḷa Rājarāja, A.D. 1149.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 10[71], <hi rend="italic">Uttarāyaṇa Sankrānti</hi> (A.D. 1149).</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of a lamp and refers to Paṇḍayārāja and Komma-nāyaka.</p>						

